Subject: Not able to access Published Reports
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: The account used to run the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor Web Server service does not have access to the Enterprise Auditor database.
What_We_Know__c:
The customer has recently upgraded NEA. It appears that the account used to Access NEA didn't had permissions on SQL server. This KB article was shared with customer after initial probing:

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/z-kb-articles-salesforce/page/kA0Qk0000000Qs9KAE.html
Next_Steps__c: Close the case as issue has been resolved.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
When you were trying to access the Web Reporting console of Netwrix Enterprise Auditor, the page would not open.

Resolution
As you mentioned that you have recently upgraded the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor and after that you were unable to access the reporting module, following the steps mentioned in this KB article resolved the issue for you:

Unable to View Published Reports in Web Console
